        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer747143223" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6251976937357274743">It&apos;s the first short story collection I finished like a novel and liked a lot! Meghna Pant is one of my favourite authors (I really liked One &amp; a Half Wife)and in Happy Birthday she creates magic with beautiful short stories. Her neat, crisp and interestingly &apos;natural&apos; style of writing makes this book a smooth &amp; engrossing read! I&apos;m really impressed!</span>
  <span id="freeText6251976937357274743" style="display:none">It's the first short story collection I finished like a novel and liked a lot! Meghna Pant is one of my favourite authors (I really liked One &amp; a Half Wife)and in Happy Birthday she creates magic with beautiful short stories. Her neat, crisp and interestingly 'natural' style of writing makes this book a smooth &amp; engrossing read! I'm really impressed!</span>
